@@yCondemn@@W                                              Sentinel level 45

Syntax: condemn

Formally denounce your current target, applying a WIS-scaled debuff that
reduces saves and AC for 5 rounds. Requires 3 or more testimony marks
against the target — you need sufficient observation before pronouncing
judgment.

@@yDetails:@@W
  * Mana cost: 15
  * Saves penalty: WIS / 3 (7 at WIS 22).
  * AC penalty: WIS / 2 (11 at WIS 22).
  * Does NOT consume testimony marks — they remain for a future verdict.
  * Cannot stack (one condemn at a time per target).

The condemn-then-verdict sequence is the Sentinel's peak burst: condemn to
lower saves, then deliver a high-mark verdict for maximum impact.

See also: @@msentinel verdict testimony@@W
